HEADWORD: Formosan
<hw>Formosan</hw> <pos>prop. adj.</pos> <def>of, pertaining to, or
characteristic of, Formosa or the natives of Formosa; <as>as, The native
<ex>Formosan</ex> population now forms a minority on their own
island.</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Taiwanese, Chinese.</syn>⟦br⟧
